plot: When drama at Danielle's mozzarella party eases after an unexpected olive branch from Teresa, all is seemingly fine until Louie and Joe go head-to-head at Guys Night. While Bill fails to make Jennifer feel better after things with Dolores and Margaret go from bad to worse, Teresa's daughters are upset after hearing Melissa and Joe's podcast in which hurtful accusations about the past are brought to light. Rachel and John struggle to get on the same page about how many kids they want. Dolores finds herself stuck between Paulie and Frank in an awkward encounter.—Anonymous
